  title: Larry is Dead
  description: "*sob* Hello? My poor computer, Larry, *sob* horrifically exploded,
    so I\u2019m arranging a funeral service for it. It didn't have too many friends,
    so I\u2019d really appreciate it if you could send some mechs over to cry at
    the procession. Otherwise, Larry will be far too lonely, and I just couldn\u2019t
    bear that! Please help this grieving man honor his best friend."
